MM8DRead - Status reader program for MM8D device
------------------------------------------------

1. About software
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
  You can check status of MM8D growing house controllers with this
software via network.

2. How to get installer package for my OS?
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
a. Visit homepage (see later) to download installer packages:

  architecture  operation system        filename
  --------------------------------------------------------------------
  (all)         (source code)           mm8dread-0.2.tar.gz
  armhf         Raspbian OS             mm8dread_0.2-1_armhf.deb
  armhf         Linux                   mm8dread-0.2-armhf.bin
  armhf         Linux                   mm8dread-0.2-armhf.tar.gz
  i386          Debian GNU/Linux        mm8dread_0.2-1_i386.deb
  i586          Linux                   mm8dread-0.2-i586.bin
  i586          Linux                   mm8dread-0.2-i586.tar.gz
  i586          Windows 32 bit          mm8dread-0.2-win32.exe
  i586          Windows 32 bit          mm8dread-0.2-win32.msi
  i586          Windows 32 bit          mm8dread-0.2-win32.zip

b. Download from Github

  $ git clone https://github.com/pozsarzs/mm8dread.git

c. Download from Debian repository

  set reporitory:
  # echo "deb http://www.szerafingomba.hu/deb/ ./" >> /etc/apt/sources.list
  # wget -q -O - http://www.szerafingomba.hu/deb/KEY.gpg | apt-key add -
  # apt-get update

  install
  # apt-get install mm8dread

